snippet.title: Early Access Trailer | VEILED EXPERTS
snippet.description:
Get ready for your new favorite go-to shooter — #VEILEDEXPERTS
VEILED EXPERTS returns as an Early Access title on May 18.
Wishlist Now on Steam : https://nexon.link/5eM
 

—


📆 Early Access release times :

▶ PT: 5/18 20:00 (Pacific Time)
▶ ET: 5/18 23:00 (Eastern Time)
▶ BRT: 5/19 00:00 (Brasilia Time)
▶ UTC: 5/19 03:00
▶ BST: 5/19 04:00 (British Summer Time)
▶ CEST: 5/19 05:00 (Central European Summer Time)
▶ CST: 5/19 11:00 (China Standard Time)
▶ KST: 5/19 12:00 (Korea Standard Time)
▶ AET: 5/19 13:00 (Australian Eastern Time)


—


VEILED EXPERTS is a Free-to-Play 5v5 tactical shooter where agents with unique Lepton skills meet action-packed gun mechanics.

Follow us on our Social Media for more updates and event notices:
Discord : https://discord.gg/veiledexperts
Twitter: https://twitter.com/VeiledExperts
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/VEILEDEXPERTS
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/veiledexperts/

#EARLYACCESS #MAY18
